目前的死神界，乃是由小丑派系所統御。祂們高壓統治眾死神，並強行流放異己。被流放的死神們心有不甘，於是秘密集結，意圖透過神秘的獻祭儀式奪回對死神界的掌控。然而，儀式的集會所早已被小丑派系滲透，不僅獻祭的順序被打亂，就連祭品的真實身分也無法辨識！眼看就要錯過儀式發動的時機，流放者們只得和小丑決一「死」戰&hellip;&hellip;

《生死逆謀》是一款陣營心機遊戲。玩家將扮演「流放者」或「小丑」，透過「獻祭」並且「發動儀式」以取得勝利。遊戲中有許多資訊是隱藏的，但又有許多環節需要投票表決，因此玩家在任何時候都可以自由發言，透過討論、協商或是話術以獲得資訊，幫助己方陣營推理並有策略的投票。當然，玩家也可以選擇不透露資訊、或是提供錯誤資訊，利用資訊落差製造己方陣營的優勢。

Additional hero for the game The Dwarves.

&bdquo;Djerun is, like all acronta, able to let his eyes flash up in a violet light, which will terrify almost all kinds of creatures. He is wearing an armour made of tionium (tionium is a black metal). His helmet&rsquo;s visor resembles a grotesque demon&rsquo;s face. Djerun is carrying a club, an axe, a sword and a serrated shield.&ldquo;

In the The Dwarves Big Box is already enough space for the two new characters Djerun and Goimgar. You will then have 14 different miniatures to choose from.

In the game, you get 144 cards, split into 2 decks of Chances (really good scoring chances), and Half-Chances (long shot scoring chances). Teams are rated simply for goals scored and goals allowed, home and away. Each team is rated further for who scores the team's goals when a goal is scored.

Depending on the goals scored rating of the team and the goals allowed rating of the opponent, each team will get a certain number of possible chances per game. The trick is that not all those chances will come up in a game and, despite having more possible total chances in a match than the opposition, a streak of bad luck could lead to the big upset. Players roll two six sided dice, one to see if anything happens in that period of time (1 out of six times you get a Chance, 1 out of six you get a Half Chance, 4 out of six you get nothing ).  You roll each half of the match until you run out of possible chances.

Example: one team has 7 chances, the other team has 3. There will be a total of 10 dice rolls to make up a single half of play. If you roll a 5 or 6, flip a FAC and a further roll of the dice will happen to determine the outcome.

The Chance and Half-Chance cards have descriptive play calls on them so you really get the feel of watching the highlights reel of a match. You will have high scoring shootouts and defensive stalemates.

Included are:

    124 Team Indicator cards which are used to identify and rate the *128 competing teams;
    16 dice of various colors which are used to determine the shots missed and the goals scored during the game. A team rating determines the number of dice rolled - a five might be a goal while a 6 is always a goal;
    a Match Die Chart to cross-reference against the ratings for each team;
    a Goal Misses Chart, which adds imagery;
    a Goal Description Chart, which also adds to the imagery;
    a Rule Book; and a description of how to convert the F. A. Cup system to various sized leagues.


The game also requires a deck of regular playing cards which you can order with the game or supply yourself.

&mdash;user summary

What is a mile&hellip; What is a mimosa&hellip; What is a millennial? It&rsquo;s a pretty common question on Google. The millennial generation has generated more intrigue than any other. And rightly so in our opinion. That&rsquo;s why we created Millennial AF: the &ldquo;Who&rsquo;s most likely to&rdquo; card game that&rsquo;ll reveal the biggest bottomless brunching, quinoa munching, Insta-influencing millennial in your group.

Here&rsquo;s how it might play out&hellip;
Jess: &ldquo;Who&rsquo;s most likely to&hellip; text &lsquo;I&rsquo;m outside&rsquo; rather than ring the doorbell?
Josh: &ldquo;Well that can&rsquo;t be me. I&rsquo;d never do that.&rdquo;
Sam: &ldquo;That&rsquo;s totes something you&rsquo;d do, Josh!&rdquo;
Jess: &ldquo;Josh IMHO.&rdquo;
George: &ldquo;Josh. Without a doubt.&rdquo;
Josh: &ldquo;WTF?!&rdquo;

Josh then gets that card. And at the end each player tallies their cards; the one with the most is the most millennial of them all.

Millennial AF is the generational game based on typical millennial traits. You&rsquo;ll be surprised at just how millennial we all are&hellip;

A band of outlaws have taken to hiding out in the forests around Carcassonne, stealing from the rich
and giving it to the poor. Or at least that&rsquo;s how the story goes&hellip;

A brawling tournament takes place among who has the majority of Woodsman in the forest with the Merry Men Camp. Who will get to be the Champion of the brawling will get 2 points for each forest tile. Moreover, the player who completes the largest Forest will get 1 point for each completed forest at the end of the game.

Shipwrecked! is a semi-cooperative survival game for up to 4 players. Taking control of &lsquo;Brains&rsquo; and &lsquo;Brawn&rsquo;, players will explore a mysterious island inhabited by pirates, dinosaurs and monsters.

By working together and combining their skills, Brains and Brawn can craft useful tools and weapons that will help them defeat the toughest enemies, and survive long enough to repair the ship and escape. But temptation and betrayal is never far away&hellip;

The goal is to escape before the unstable volcano erupts and destroys the island, but the ultimate winner is the one who makes it out alive with the most treasure. It&rsquo;s survival of the fittest...and richest!

The company entered bankruptcy during this project and comments in the crowdfunding campaign indicate that crowdfunded versions were never delivered.  It appears a shipment of games was offered in retail in France/Germany starting in 2023.  The 2023 retail version currently avalable does not include any Kickstarted expansions. 


Tiles of the Arabian Nights is set in the universe of the Arabian Nights. In Bagdad, storytelling has become deeply ingrained in the city&rsquo;s culture ever since the legendary Scheherazade told 1001 unforgettable tales over as many nights. In honor of the queen, the Sultan now holds a storytelling contest each year!This year, as a citizen of Bagdad, you&rsquo;re taking part in the contest, in the hopes of winning the title of Master Storyteller. But coming up with a good story isn&rsquo;t easy, and as every tale contains at least a grain of truth, you find yourself in search of a little inspiration&hellip;

So get ready to head out into the desert in search of adventure! As you explore, you&rsquo;ll meet colorful characters, find amazing treasures, and defeat fearsome foes. Each new discovery you make will earn you an Adventure tile. Once you&rsquo;ve collected enough tiles for your story, you&rsquo;ll return to Bagdad to tell it to the awaiting crowds.

Exactly what your story will be is up to you&hellip;

Use the beautiful, unique illustrations on your tiles as inspiration to come up with a story worthy of the Arabian Nights! Each tale you tell will earn you points from the Sultan himself, and from other players. The player with the most points at the end of the game wins!

&mdash;description from the publisher
